Kazian Ministry of Defence has chosen 123 of its prettiest female soldiers and posted their photos online where viewers can vote for their favourites . 
  Pictures show the women in three set poses – in military uniform, with weapons and in civilian clothing – and have been viewed more than 30,000 times . 
  Military officials hope the competition will encourage more recruits . 
  Sergeant Aigerim Karakuchukova is the front-runner so far with more than 1,100 votes  . 
 